Enum nvinfer.ElementWiseOperation

    @Namespace(value="nvinfer1")
public static enum nvinfer.ElementWiseOperation
extends Enum<nvinfer.ElementWiseOperation>
    \enum ElementWiseOperation \brief Enumerates the binary operations that may be performed by an ElementWise layer. Operations kAND, kOR, and kXOR must have inputs of DataType::kBOOL. All other operations must have inputs of floating-point type, DataType::kINT8, DataType::kINT32, or DataType::kINT64.
    See Also:
    IElementWiseLayer
